---
layout: page.njk
---
{% if heroImage %}
<div class="home-hero-wrapper">
  <div class="home-slideshow-fs">
    <img src="{{ heroImage }}" alt="{{ title }}" class="img-cover">
  </div>
  <section class="home-hero-overlay">
    <h1 class="home-title">{{ title }}</h1>
    {% if description %}<p class="home-intro">{{ description }}</p>{% endif %}
    <div class="scroll-hint">
      <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M7 13l5 5 5-5M7 6l5 5 5-5"/></svg>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
{% endif %}

<div class="standard-page">

  <!-- Why buy -->
  <p class="section-label">Why Buy From Me?</p>
  <div class="skills-grid prints-why-grid">

    <div class="skill-card prints-why-card">
      <div class="prints-why-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h4>Exclusive & Flexible</h4>
      <p>Every print is one of a kind — you'll be the only person who ever owns a printed copy, backed by a certificate of exclusivity. Choose to receive a physical print shipped to your door, or a full resolution digital file with a print release for unlimited personal printing.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="skill-card prints-why-card">
      <div class="prints-why-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h4>Local Photographs</h4>
      <p>Each image comes from somewhere meaningful — somewhere you might know, love, or have stood yourself. I place emphasis on connecting local people with photographs of local places.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="skill-card prints-why-card">
      <div class="prints-why-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h4>Prints For Conservation</h4>
      <p>20% of every sale is donated to a conservation charity relevant to the species or landscape in the photograph. You take the credit for the donation if you wish — I just facilitate it.</p>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- Print options -->
  <p class="section-label" style="margin-top:3rem;">Print Options</p>
  <div class="prints-options-grid">

    <div class="prints-option-card">
      <div class="prints-option-header">
        <div class="prints-option-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="1" y="3" width="15" height="13" rx="1"/><path d="M16 8h4l3 3v5h-7V8z"/><circle cx="5.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"/><circle cx="18.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="prints-option-label">Option 1</p>
          <h3 class="prints-option-title">Printed & Shipped</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="prints-option-desc">I handle printing through a professional lab and ship the finished photograph directly to you, printed on premium archival paper and ready to frame.</p>
      <ul class="prints-option-list">
        <li>Professional print lab quality</li>
        <li>Archival, fade-resistant paper</li>
        <li>Multiple size options available</li>
        <li>Exclusivity certificate included</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="prints-option-card prints-option-featured">
      <div class="prints-option-badge">Most Popular</div>
      <div class="prints-option-header">
        <div class="prints-option-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="prints-option-label">Option 2</p>
          <h3 class="prints-option-title">Digital File & Print Release</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="prints-option-desc">Receive the full resolution digital file with a print release agreement — print anywhere, any size, as many times as you like for personal use.</p>
      <ul class="prints-option-list">
        <li>Full resolution master file</li>
        <li>Unlimited personal use prints</li>
        <li>Print at any lab, any size</li>
        <li>Exclusivity certificate included</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>

